<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="14Jul1936"><font color="red">14 July 1936</font> <i>NLJL</i> (from Edward Young of the Bodley Head to Paul L&eacute;on): Tuesday. Our reader has sent us another batch of queries, which you will find on the accompanying sheet. </div>
